          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--color-accent); font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent); padding-left: 8px;">Writing & Mentoring</h3>
          <div class="simple-list">
            <div class="simple-list-item">
              <span class="label">Columnist</span>
              <span class="detail">— <a href="https://www.nia.or.kr/site/nia_kor/ex/bbs/List.do?cbIdx=99863" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NIA Cloud Service Trend Report</a> (monthly)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="simple-list-item">
              <span class="label">Mentor</span>
              <span class="detail">— Kernel360 4th Cohort</span>
